The '''Swirblies''' were a group of deities of the [[Skakoan religion]] that lived in the [[Gates of Grontessiant]]. They were ruled by a [[Lord Being of the Swirblies|Lord Being]], and possibly included the [[Four See Seers of the Cyclops|See Seers]].

